Package: directCareAnalytics
Title: Financial Analytics Dashboard for Direct Care Practices
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Anthony W.", "Raborn", , "anthony@raborndecisionsciences.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Golem-based Shiny dashboard that wraps the directCareForecastR
    backend to provide an interactive interface for uploading practice financial
    data, reviewing and correcting transactions, and generating revenue and
    break-even forecasts with downloadable branded reports.
